com.samsung.android.sdk.pen.document.textspan

Class SpenHyperTextSpan

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.samsung.android.sdk.pen.document.textspan.SpenTextSpanBase
      • com.samsung.android.sdk.pen.document.textspan.SpenHyperTextSpan

  • public final class SpenHyperTextSpan
extends SpenTextSpanBase
    SpenHyperTextSpan class.
    This class extends SpenTextSpanBase.
    This class is created automatically if the text has some hypertext. User can't create this class. This class is created by "SpenObjectShape.parseHyperText()".
    Since:
    4.0.0
